    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I think the point is to check if something can grant that upgrade, not to check if the source and user can meet ingame to actually interact.\n\nIt's like prerequisites - I don't think we check if actor A, that grants prerequisite B is actually buildable, we just check that there is an actor that grants that prerequisite.\n"
